content: Beacon Health reimbursement form 4892-6RQ details 12 weeks of physical therapy for Miranda Kjeldsen (patient ID BKJ-227H) at Boston Spine & Joint Clinic. Treatment includes aquatic therapy and kinesio taping protocols for hypermobile Ehlers-Danlos syndrome. Authored by Dr. Ellen Park on 06/15/2023 with referral from Dr. Amir Gupta at Commonwealth Cardiology.
